com.io7m.jspatial.quadtrees

Class QuadTreePrune<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.io7m.jspatial.quadtrees.QuadTreePrune<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of objects contained within the tree.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    QuadTreeType<T>

    public final class QuadTreePrune<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>
extends Object
implements QuadTreeType<T>

    A quadtree implementation based on QuadTreeBasic but implementing empty node pruning when an object is removed from the tree.

    An implementation that aggressively removes empty nodes from the tree increases garbage collection pressure, but reduces the number of nodes that must be traversed when enumerating objects. This improves the performance of area and raycast queries.
